name: Jamie Lopez
summary: Jamie Lopez is a 31-year-old, non-binary, gay individual from San Diego, California. Their ethnicity is Hispanic/Latino and their pronouns are they/them/their. Professionally, they are a Registered Nurse in the Healthcare industry after graduating from the University of California, Los Angeles. Jamie currently resides in Los Angeles and they actively speak English and Spanish. They highly value honesty, empathy, and respect. They enjoy yoga, traveling, and cooking. While they are agnostic and lean politically liberal, they are actively looking for a life partner interested in monogamy. They don’t have any children but would like to have in the future. They own a dog, don't smoke but drink occasionally. With an active lifestyle, Jamie is a Libra and identifies as ENFP according to the MBTI personality type. As per their preferences, they are open to meeting gay men who are between 29 and 40 years old, are active, don't smoke, but may drink, and are considering having children in the future.
